# ThoughtSpot: Coach a Model (Comprehensive Spotter Preparation)

Prepare a ThoughtSpot Model for Spotter across five coaching surfaces:

| Surface | Where it lives | What it does |
|---|---|---|
| Column AI Context | `model.columns[].properties.ai_context` (≤ 400 chars per column) | Per-column meaning — Spotter's primary disambiguation signal |
| Column Synonyms | `model.columns[].synonyms[]` | Schema-level alternative names; the parser substitutes them |
| Reference Questions | `nls_feedback.feedback[type=REFERENCE_QUESTION]` | Whole-question → tokenised-search mappings |
| Business Terms | `nls_feedback.feedback[type=BUSINESS_TERM]` | Phrase → existing column or formula |
| Data Model Instructions | Model-level free text (TML location TBD) | Global rules ("when I say last month, use last 30 days") |

Existing AI assets are critiqued + improved, never silently overwritten. The user
picks which surfaces to generate via a single up-front menu.

Ask one question at a time. Wait for each answer before proceeding.

