## Common errors

| Symptom | Action |
|---|---|
| `ts auth whoami` returns 401 | Token expired — refresh profile |
| Selected data source is a Worksheet | Recommend upgrading to Model first; stop |
| ai_context > 400 chars | Reduce — drop axes in priority order: excludes → includes → null_zero → time_basis → unit |
| `Invalid value token: <kw>` on feedback import | Bad search_tokens syntax — see verified patterns above; common mistake is `top 10` AFTER columns instead of before |
| `EDOC_FEEDBACK_TML_INVALID — Search did not find <expr>` | `formula_info` on RQ — drop the question or use Model-formula workaround |
| `chart_type: TABLE` rejected | Use `chart_type: COLUMN` + `display_mode: TABLE_MODE` instead |

